{"tid":2432241,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有spotify嘅巴打絲打 loop下榮光","createTime":"2021-03-04T07:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T20:32:13.000Z","uid":386426,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"339cf03f052dbe879209e7f91474f99034546e19","tid":2432241,"uid":386426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"榮光首歌2分鐘長 一個人loop夠一日就有720個play<br />\n香港spotify top 50淨係需要7,000 daily plays就入到 即係10個人全日24小時loop榮光就可以上到榜 <br />\n英國spotify top 50要100,000 daily plays就入到 即係140個人loop就上到榜<br />\n美國spotify top 50 應該唔夠人架啦，要375,000 daily plays先入到 即係525個人loop<br />\n外國嘅巴打絲打可以loop英文版 等外國人都可以聽得明<br />\n淨係需要上 spotify web player 免費 account 就可以無限loop 做緊嘢訓緊覺都可以無限loop 總之部電腦著咗就得架啦，loop緊個陣做乜都得總之唔好閂咗個tab就得架啦<br />\n其他音樂平台我唔係好熟，不過有就loop吓啦，上咗top 50就應該更加多人會搵到呢首歌 支持下香港人"},{"pid":"872456d62c90f49e47a75139ca3515fbcfd10d29","tid":2432241,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:28:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30c3b4457f928722b65db15472801fa5bdc76114","tid":2432241,"uid":1627,"like":6,"dislike":30,"score":-24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:37:12.000Z","msg":"咁難聽仲要loop成日"},{"pid":"0d49a92d1fdb1a68b71eff81c72ff46564e22177","tid":2432241,"uid":96231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30c3b4457f928722b65db15472801fa5bdc76114","tid":2432241,"uid":1627,"like":6,"dislike":30,"score":-24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:37:12.000Z","msg":"咁難聽仲要loop成日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"有得爭取運動曝光嘅我哋應該都要爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：apple music同Spotify都有嘅用家"},{"pid":"c1b287ec4e8c4cfb8fa0a9f474a5a266251914d1","tid":2432241,"uid":386426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30c3b4457f928722b65db15472801fa5bdc76114","tid":2432241,"uid":1627,"like":6,"dislike":30,"score":-24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:37:12.000Z","msg":"咁難聽仲要loo